vsParam:
Oh, so this place is called the Bressisle, huh.
It's entirely different from my world.

Ah, I am Wilbell!
I am new to this strange place... Nice to meet you!

Sure, nice to meet you, too! I mean,
you are dressed like a witch from a storybook!

No! I, I am not, what are you saying?
I couldn't... understand...

Don't, don't talk wildly! No witch would be
bold enough to dress as a witch.

Hmm, it's pretty common, no?
Majorum Sensei dresses like that.

Ah. You are a witch, Witch.
Why don't you say that earlier?

*Boo-hoo*, I didn't expect to get exposed so quickly...
Aren't you shocked!?

Hmm... I wanted to ask you why are you shocked.
I am a student of Wizardology.

... Uh, Wizardology?
So, witches and wizards are common in this world, huh?

B, bravo!
I thought I'll get scolded by grandmother again...
Wilbell, are you trying to conceal your identity as a witch?

Yes. In my world,
witches and wizards must hide their identities.

Because wizardry has great powers, we purposely hide it
to prevent it from falling in the wrong hands.

But wizardry is quite common here... Does it mean that
I can use wizardry whenever I want?

Ha ha, so excited, huh?...
Are you so eager to use wizardry, Wilbell?

Of course! Although I am still cultivating,
I aspire to become a great witch someday!

Ah, Wilbell, why don't stay at the Academy?
It has a Wizardology Department!

That's right. Joining the Wizardology Department
will greatly help with your cultivation.

Er... hmm, that sounds wonderful.
Then I'll stay because of my kindness.

Sure, it's settled!
Please help and support each other, Wilbell!
